  "steps": [
    "Cut tissue into small pieces.",
    "Digestion of ca. 25 mg sample with Buffer ATL (Qiagen, Hilden, DE) and Proteinase K overnight at 56 °C. undetermined, Sample Incubation was performed on a thermomixer with 800 rpm",
    "After pelleting remaining material, remove supernatant and added to Buffer AL and ethanol.",
    "Transfer the solution to DNeasy Mini spin column (Qiagen, Hilden, DE) and centrifuge at 8000 rpm.",
    "DNA purification following manufacturer&#39;s protocol with Buffer AW1 and Buffer AW2 (Qiagen, Hilden, DE).",
    "Prior to elution, incubate DNA in the membrane with elution Buffer AE for 5 min at room temperature. 00:05:00, Incubation at RT",
    "Elution proceeds by centrifugation at 8000 rpm for 1 min. 00:01:00, Centrifugation",
    "Measure DNA concentration on Nanodrop (Thermo Fischer Scientific, Darmstadt, DE)."
